TITLE UUTransition Over Manual Loading States
UUTRANSITION OVER MANUAL LOADING STATES
UUTransition IO manual useState for loading states. This provides built-in isPending state and automatically manages transitions. 
Incorrect (manual loading state): 
CODE tsx 520CHARS
Correct (useTransition with built-in pending state): 
CODE tsx 631CHARS
Benefits: 
Automatic pending state: No need to manually manage setIsLoading(true/false) Error resilience: Pending state correctly resets even if the transition throws Better responsiveness: Keeps the UI responsive during updates Interrupt handling: New transitions automatically cancel pending ones 
REFERENCE [useTransition](https://react.dev/reference/react/useTransition)